com.okta.scim.util.model

Class Membership

  • Object
    • com.okta.scim.util.model.Membership

  • public class Membership
extends Object
    Used to represent a membership or link to another object.

    When used in the SCIMGroup class, the getMembers method returns a collection of users that are a member of that group. The id will contain the user's unique id, and the displayName will contain the formatted displayName of the user.

    When used in the SCIMUser class, the getGroup method returns a collection of groups that contain that user as a member. The id will contain the group's unique id, and the displayName will contain the displayName of the group.
